reviewText: not really all that good, just wanted to be the first four star review. Probably a 2!

This sucks. It started out okay, but when they start depicting the behavior of a pot smoker...shut up! I turned this off when it reminded me of 1980s weed documentaries. Totally unrealistic view of the lifestyled.

Great story line! Very informitive of California weed scene. Will educate while entertaining you. A good film for all - no matter what side of the issue you are on. Some use of strong language, not appropiate for children. Sometimes funny, sometimes sad, never boring.
Wasn't expecting a documentary, but very informative.
Fun, lighthearted film about what it's like to be a cannabis user in CA. Well worth watching-- Ix, the "star" of the film, is a real delight! Shows the ups and downs in a never too preachy way.
Not very good for a stoner documentary, it mainly follows an overly theatrical spazzy attention seeking girl, who's mildly hot at best.  I'd recomend Super High Me or a stoner comedy instead.
